OpenEmbedded/Yocto BSP layer for chainer
=============================================

This layer provides chainer recipes for use with OpenEmbedded
and/or Yocto.

This layer inherits pypi and setuptools recipe.

Contributing
------------

Bug reports and pull requests are welcome on GitHub at https://github.com/clear-code/meta-chainer.

For Yocto 2.0(jethro), please consider to use [rz-g1-numpy](https://github.com/clear-code/meta-chainer/tree/rz-g1-numpy) branch.